OL,3,CSikh charity spreads joy and happiness
OL,4,Cwith its Christmas gifts and food
OL,5,Cparcels
OL,7,FThe Sikh community at the Gurdwara
OL,8,FBaba Vadbhag Singh Ji (BVS) in
OL,9,FCoventry are spreading joy this
OL,10,FChristmas with presents and food so
OL,11,Fthat everyone has something to unwrap
OL,12,Fand treats to enjoy on the 25th.
OL,14,FThe BVS charity have been collecting
OL,15,Fand buying children's toys and games
OL,16,Fsince September and in recent weeks
OL,17,Fhave been busy wrapping and putting
OL,18,Ftogether hundreds of parcels and
OL,19,Fhampers.
