OL,8,Fsaid:"Christmas is a time full of
OL,9,Fhappiness but it's also a time where
OL,10,Fpeople feel most lonely.
OL,12,F"People feel that financial stress and
OL,13,Fthe mission of our founder Kulvinder
OL,14,FSingh is to send joy and happiness to
OL,15,Fall those houses. This year the
OL,16,Fproject is impacting around 2000
OL,17,Fpeople."
