OL,7,FThe Christmas project has been running
OL,8,Fsince 2017 with the number of people
OL,9,Fthey help growing every year. This
OL,10,Ftime round the gifts have been
OL,11,Fdelivered to nine schools and family
OL,12,Fcentres in Coventry and Warwickshire
OL,13,Fat a cost of around #50,000.
OL,15,FUp until now, the effort has been self-
OL,16,Ffunded but this year Warwickshire
OL,17,FCounty Council also gave some
OL,18,Ffinancial support.
