OL,7,FLindsay Eardley, headteacher at St
OL,8,FPaul's C Of E school in Nuneaton which
OL,9,Fhad a delivery from the Gurdwara, said
OL,10,Fof the families receiving the
OL,11,Fpresents: "They're absolutely
OL,12,Foverwhelmed that people are doing this
OL,13,Ffor them, that people are that kind.
OL,15,F"It just makes their Christmases
OL,16,Fbecause that worry has just
OL,17,Fdisappeared, they don't need to worry
OL,18,Fanymore. It's about feeling loved and
OL,19,Fthey couldn't be more grateful."
